PN,43201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe inquest into the death of a mother-
OL,8,Fof-five who died after undergoing a
OL,9,FBrazilian butt lift (BBL) is likely to
OL,10,Ftake place later this year.
OL,12,FAlice Webb, 33, died in September 2024
OL,13,Fafter receiving the BBL procedure at a
OL,14,Fsalon in Gloucester.
OL,16,FA pre-inquest review at
OL,17,FGloucestershire Coroner's Court heard
OL,18,Fthat the man who carried out the
OL,19,Fprocedure, Jordan Parke, has himself
OL,20,Fsince died.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FMs Webb, from Wotton-under-Edge, had
OL,8,Ffallen ill following the cosmetic
OL,9,Ftreatment and was taken to
OL,10,FGloucestershire Royal Hospital where
OL,11,Fshe later died.
OL,13,FPolice launched a criminal
OL,14,Finvestigation and a man and woman were
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of manslaughter.
OL,17,FThe woman was later released without
OL,18,Fcharge, and the investigation was
OL,19,Fcontinuing until Mr Parke ` dubbed the
OL,20,F"British Lip King" ` died in February
OL,21,Fthis year.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FIt is believed he may have been
OL,8,Fundergoing a cosmetic procedure prior
OL,9,Fto his death in Canary Wharf, London.
OL,11,FMr Parke had appeared on television
OL,12,Fshows including ITV's This Morning to
OL,13,Fdiscuss cosmetic surgery he had
OL,14,Fpreviously undergone.
OL,16,FKaty Skerrett, senior coroner for
OL,17,FGloucestershire, said a full inquest
OL,18,Fwould take place in the autumn and
OL,19,Fwould last around three days.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FLaura Collignon, representing Ms
OL,8,FWebb's family, submitted to the
OL,9,Fcoroner that the inquest should take
OL,10,Fplace in front of a jury because her
OL,11,Fdeath was workplace related.
OL,13,F"From speaking to the family, but also
OL,14,Ffrom looking through the records from
OL,15,Fyour office, Alice was engaged in some
OL,16,Ftraining because she undertook these
OL,17,Fsorts of procedures herself," she said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"She was not only there having a
OL,8,Fprocedure, she was being trained in a
OL,9,Fprocedure, and that seems to me to be
OL,10,Fa workplace matter, and therefore a
OL,11,Fworkplace fatality, and that would be
OL,12,Fnotifiable.
OL,14,F"That would mean that a jury would be
OL,15,Frequired."
OL,17,FIn reply, the coroner said: "My
OL,18,Finitial view is that Alice was a self-
OL,19,Femployed practitioner and she was
OL,20,Fbeing shown how to do a procedure at a
OL,21,Ffriend's house.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUwD@JO]yD@]OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"I think you could probably argue it
OL,8,Feither way. I'm content that it should
OL,9,Fbe in front of a jury."
OL,11,FMs Skerrett said the inquest would
OL,12,Fhear evidence from police, a
OL,13,Fpathologist, as well the woman who ran
OL,14,Fthe salon, Jemma Pawlyszyn, and
OL,15,Fanother person who was present before
OL,16,FMs Webb fell ill.
OL,18,F"There were some other people who were
OL,19,Fpresent and you will probably be aware
OL,20,Fthat Jordan Parke himself has died,"
OL,21,FMiss Collignon said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@WO]zD@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"He's the person who carried out the
OL,8,Fprocedure, but there were two women
OL,9,Fwho were present.
OL,11,F"Jemma Pawlyszyn, and it was her
OL,12,Fpremises, and there was another woman
OL,13,Fwho was there, who was also
OL,14,Fundertaking the training, and I'm told
OL,15,Fthat the police have her identity.
OL,17,F"That is something I would have
OL,18,Fexpected, given that Jordan Parke has
OL,19,Fdied and there is not an ongoing
OL,20,Fcriminal investigation, that that file
OL,21,Fwould probably be available to you.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"It would be possible for you to
OL,8,Fidentify that person, and to ask that
OL,9,Fperson to attend, since they were
OL,10,Factually present at the time.
OL,12,F"She was apparently, as far as the
OL,13,Ffamily know, not present when Alice
OL,14,Fbecame unwell, but she had been there
OL,15,Fearlier in the day having the
OL,16,Fprocedure, which was videoed, and the
OL,17,Fpolice have the video of the procedure
OL,18,Fbeing carried out on her.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"We don't know at what point she left
OL,8,Fthe premises. It seems to me that it
OL,9,Fis relevant given that Mr Parke then
OL,10,Fperformed the same procedure on Alice,
OL,11,Fas far as we know."
OL,13,FFollowing Ms Webb's death, campaigners
OL,14,Fhave called for the regulation of the
OL,15,Fbeauty industry and for certain
OL,16,Fcosmetic procedures to be banned.
OL,18,FThe Government has announced proposals
OL,19,Fto make sure that BBLs and other high-
OL,20,Frisk procedures are only performed by
OL,21,Fspecified health workers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FSeveral members of her family,
OL,8,Fincluding mother and brother, were
OL,9,Fpresent during the hearing.
OL,11,FSpeaking afterwards, Ms Webb's former
OL,12,Fpartner Ben Kingscote called on the
OL,13,FGovernment to ban certain procedures.
OL,15,F"They are talking and they are warning
OL,16,Fpeople, but they are not actually
OL,17,Fdoing anything," he said.
OL,19,F"They need to pull their fingers out
OL,20,Fand get it banned before someone else
OL,21,Fdies."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@PO]{D@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FFollowing the death of Mr Parke,
OL,8,FGloucestershire Police said: "A woman
OL,9,Fwas later told she faced no further
OL,10,Fpolice action, and a man remained on
OL,11,Fpolice bail while further enquiries
OL,12,Fwere taking place.
OL,14,F"We have been informed that the man
OL,15,Fwho was on police bail died recently,
OL,16,Fand therefore the criminal
OL,17,Finvestigation will close as no charges
OL,18,Fcan be brought.
OL,26,@pD@^OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779123960
OL,3,CInquest into death of mother-of-five
OL,4,Cafter BBL procedure likely later this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"Police enquiries will continue on
OL,8,Fbehalf of the coroner, and an inquest
OL,9,Fwill take place in due course to try
OL,10,Fand establish what happened."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
